Psychic Development 2

January 8th and 22nd - February 5th and 19th 2013

7pm - 9pm

Presented by Lisa Campion







Psychic Development Two

Did you know that we all have a team of spirit guides working with us? These benevolent beings are invested in helping us on all levels of our growth. In this exciting and informative class you will learn all about your spirit guides as well as the fundamental skills to communicate with them.

Everyone can do this. Really!

Learn which psychic channels are already open for you

Make contact with your own spirit guides right on the first class!

Explore the different types of guides, including angels, masters, power animals, earth spirits, ancestor guides and much more.

Discover easy ways to bring this guidance into your every day life

This is an entry level class, but is also suited people of all levels of psychic development.

For more information email solsticehealing@yahoo.com or Call 508-533-0669
